article_title: More Search Warrants Served At Drug House After Toddler Wanders - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Logan County deputies are back at the home of two parents whose toddler was found wandering in the middle of the street Tuesday.

Today, deputies are serving more search warrants at the home after they said they found drugs and paraphernalia, Tuesday.

News 9’s Lacie Lowry will have more on this story tonight at 5 p.m.
